## 7. UX/UI Design Notes

- Emotions shown as colorful buttons or icons.
- Content suggestions in card-style widgets, vertically stacked.
- Smooth transitions between views with fade/slide animations.
- Light theme with clean typography.


## 8. Dependencies

- SwiftUI
- AVKit / WebKit for video/audio playback
- Optional: Combine or async/await for data loading

---

## 9. Acceptance Criteria

- User sees welcome screen on launch.
- User can select emotion and receive varied, random content.
- Tapping any content opens its full view.
- No crashes or UI bugs during flow.
